main event: A civilian man sighted an object resembling a sailing ship in St. Paul, Minnesota, tracked through binoculars until lost from view due to darkness.
interesting points: The sighting occurred at 21:10 on 23/3/29., The object was described as resembling a sailing ship. The observer reported seeing a red light through binoculars., The object was tracked until it disappeared from view., The sighting was made under clear weather conditions., The report was part of the Project Blue Book documentation.
sighted object: an object resembling a sailing ship
